<DOC><DOCNO> WSJ880713-0131 </DOCNO><HL> Dividend News: Ohio Mattress Co. </HL><SO> </SO><CO> OMT </CO><IN> DIV </IN><TEXT>   OHIO MATTRESS Co. increased its quarterly to 15 cents a share from 12 cents a share and declared a 3-for-2 stock split. The new dividend, equal to 10 cents a share after adjusting for the split, is payable July 29 to holders of record July 22. </TEXT></DOC>